Rulings.Base:
1. This effect targets the Level 4 or lower "Watt" monster in your GY.
2. Destroying the monster in the End Phase does not start a Chain.
3. The Special Summoned monster will be destroyed even if your opponent controls it during the End Phase.
4. The Special Summoned monster will not be destroyed if it's flipped face-down with "Book of Moon" or temporarily removed from play and then returned with "Interdimensional Matter Transporter".
